---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import TopicLayout from '../../layouts/TopicLayout.astro';
import heaven from '../../assets/topics/heaven.png';
import hell from '../../assets/topics/hell.jpg';
---

<TopicLayout slug="afterlife">
  <p class="lede"><b>Your eternal destiny after death</b></p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      "..death is the destiny of everyone; the living should take this to heart." - Ecclesiastes 7:2
    </li>
    <li>
      "Remember your Creator in the days of your youth, before the days of trouble come and the years approach
      when you will say, “I find no pleasure in them”— Remember him—before the silver cord is severed, and the
      golden bowl is broken; before the pitcher is shattered at the spring, and the wheel broken at the well,
      and the dust returns to the ground it came from, and the spirit returns to God who gave it.""
      Ecclesiastes 12:1,6-7
    </li>
    <li>
      "Multitudes who sleep in the dust of the earth will awake: some to everlasting life, others to shame and
      everlasting contempt." - Daniel 12:2
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Which do you prefer?</h2>

  <div class="destiny-grid">
    <a href="/topics/heaven/" class="destiny-card">
      <Image src={heaven} alt="Heaven" widths={[320, 560]} sizes="(max-width: 640px) 92vw, 320px" />
      <span>Heaven</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/topics/hell/" class="destiny-card">
      <Image src={hell} alt="Hell" widths={[320, 560]} sizes="(max-width: 640px) 92vw, 320px" />
      <span>Hell</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</TopicLayout>

<style>
  .destiny-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.4rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .destiny-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .destiny-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .destiny-card img {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .destiny-card span {
    padding: 0.85rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .destiny-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
